reviews.text: Kang kong is oily and salty. Fish Maw Soup is bland. They were rude when requesting for additional plates. Experience is really bad.

Had dine-in hor fun before, was generous with it's portion and nice wok hei. They have an extensive menu, so made a note to visit again.

Today we came to buy takeaway - dried hor fun, hokkien mee and har cheong gai. Delicious!
Tasty food. Fast service. I liked their dry beef horfun
